<title>ITALY: Italian stocks open nearly two percent down.</title>
<headline>Italian stocks open nearly two percent down.</headline>
<dateline>MILAN 1997-04-01</dateline>
<text>
<p>Italy's blue-chip Mib30 index opened 1.82 percent down in the wake of falls on Wall Street, while the all-share Mibtel index began 1.86 percent lower.</p>
<p>By 0805 GMT the Mib30 index was 1.94 percent lower at 17122 and the Mibtel 1.99 percent lower at 11595.</p>
